Install maven git and tree on ec2 instance using bash


Vim installation.sh

Paste the script below



#!/bin/bash

echo "Updating Amazon Linux 2023..."
sudo dnf update -y

echo "Installing Git..."
sudo dnf install git -y

echo "Installing Java (Amazon Corretto 17)..."
sudo dnf install java-17-amazon-corretto -y

echo "Installing Maven..."
sudo dnf install maven -y

echo "Installing Tree..."
sudo dnf install tree -y

echo "Verifying installations..."
echo "----------------------------"
git --version
java -version
mvn -version
tree --version

echo "Tool setup completed successfully."



:wq to save

Launch installation by running

Sh installation.sh
